&gt; Contains an enumerator that enumerates all input that is passed to a function. The $input variable is available only to functions and script blocks (which are unnamed functions).

So changing your parameter name should work as you expect. But don&#39;t forget to also change how you call the function so it also uses the new parameter name. In this case, you can also skip the parameter name entirely when calling the function

